*Ljudska* solidarnost je nešto najvažnije u društvu. (Human solidarity is the most important thing in society.)

Kada je u pitanju *ljudsko* zdravlje, nikada nije na odmet sprovesti preventivne mere. (When it comes to human health, preventive measures are always worth taking.)

Iako se o *ljudskom* pravu na slobodu govori mnogo, taj pravni standard još uvek nije postignut. (Although much is said about human right to freedom, this legal standard has not yet been achieved.)

Političari bi trebalo da štite *ljudska* prava i da se bore za dobrobit čovečanstva. (Politicians should protect human rights and fight for the welfare of mankind.)

*Ljudskim* razumom se ne može odgovoriti na sva pitanja. (Human reason cannot answer all questions.)